{"tid":970722,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［外貌協會］每個人都有呢種超能力","createTime":"2019-01-06T05:30:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T05:48:42.000Z","uid":125420,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c0bc0900470466203df2cd107546117e9e2da9aa","tid":970722,"uid":125420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:30:11.000Z","msg":"每個人都有少少叫做「未來視」嘅超能力。<br />\n<br />\n當你望到一個異性，你就會發動能力，腦入面會出現同佢一齊之後個未來係點，可能好長，可能好短，可能係好耐之後，可能係一陣間會點。<br />\n<br />\n你會好快決定到之後同唔同對方一齊，就算依家呢刻唔想，你都會知道個結果唔係差。<br />\n<br />\n一旦你同對方一齊咗，最後係分手收場，只不過係你嘅超能力未成熟，見唔到咁遠嘅未來。<br />\n<br />\n每經歷一次戀愛，你嘅超能力就會提升少少......"},{"pid":"d97e5a64e5ff060fd89a346cf201b308e120dd3d","tid":970722,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:30:41.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"7530f28f0f9d8a04696b31c895fb550769402b04","tid":970722,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:31:19.000Z","msg":"毒撚FF完未?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ef47482b06db926306dc28947890eceb42a1db","tid":970722,"uid":72475,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:31:47.000Z","msg":"有試過<br />\n呢種應該叫ff能力"},{"pid":"b33f9853c65d198f39f9889a45ead896f07f77ea","tid":970722,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"64ef47482b06db926306dc28947890eceb42a1db","tid":970722,"uid":72475,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:31:47.000Z","msg":"有試過<br />\n呢種應該叫ff能力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:32:36.000Z","msg":"學名好似叫妄想症"},{"pid":"ffd0079dd43ee38303e75ae374b9fcb1aba586b1","tid":970722,"uid":125420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:35:04.000Z","msg":"點算，我有病，有冇邊個精神科醫生介紹？"},{"pid":"915a2b50bb6b3f6d72d11a069ccabb45b1ba6d2b","tid":970722,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":1,"scor